title: NCSoft 'Project G' - Official G-STAR 2023 Trailer
description:
Project G is a work-in-progress massive multiplayer online real-time strategy game developed by NCSoft. Players will manipulate a variety of units and bases to gain the upper hand against the enemy alongside utilizing a plethora of weapons and objects to strategically outplay the enemy in a 3D space. Project G is set to launch on mobile and PC.

title: NCSoft 'Project LLL' - Official G-STAR 2023 Trailer
description:
Project LLL is an open-world MMO third-person shooter developed by NCSoft. Players will interface with an expansive world filled with epic battles within a vast and dynamic environment. Offering a wide array of weapons and skill combinations, Project LLL aims to offer an unparalleled gameplay experience.

title: Hogwarts Legacy: How to Unlock Eye Chests
description:
Hogwarts Legacy is now available on Nintendo Switch, however, this video was made using the Xbox Series X, PlayStation 5, and PC versions of the game.

Eye Chests are non-standard chests adorned with a strange eyeball that you'll encounter many times in Hogwarts Legacy. While opening them early in the game seems impossible, they're pretty simple once you've acquired a particular basic yet helpful spell. This video will show you how to open Eyeball Chests and what mission you need to complete to start opening them.
